34
00:04:23,760 --> 00:04:25,720 
Shut up, you fuckhead!

35
00:04:26,280 --> 00:04:29,280 
- You're breaking my fucking arm!
- Hurry!

36
00:04:31,880 --> 00:04:34,240 
Look at this. What a nasty man.

37
00:04:34,440 --> 00:04:38,280 
Night's made. Let's pay Papa
and get us what we need.

38
00:04:38,480 --> 00:04:40,240 
Nuke me, baby!

39
00:04:41,560 --> 00:04:45,280 
- I'll kill you bitches!
- He's up! Come on!

40
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:53,520 
- You're shit with a timer, man!
- Come on! Let's go!

41
00:05:03,000 --> 00:05:05,600 
