47
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:51,200 
Just take it and get out.

48
00:05:51,480 --> 00:05:52,680 
Thanks.

49
00:05:57,080 --> 00:05:59,160 
- I don't believe this!
- What?

50
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:02,080 
- It's the cops, man.
- Cops are on strike, stupid.

51
00:06:02,280 --> 00:06:04,240 
Can't you hear that?

52
00:06:13,720 --> 00:06:16,840 
- See. What did I tell you?
- I'll fix him.

53
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:31,000 
Did you see that? We got him!

54
00:06:31,520 --> 00:06:35,200 
- Beautiful. Come on, man. Let's move it.
- No. One more!

55
00:06:37,000 --> 00:06:39,400 
Nice shit, man.

56
00:06:40,160 --> 00:06:42,040 
Fucking cops!

57
00:07:36,200 --> 00:07:37,400 
Peace officer.

58
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:40,920 
Think it over, creep.

59
00:07:54,960 --> 00:07:56,560 
Nuke.

60
