It's not mine, man.

61
00:08:00,640 --> 00:08:03,480 
Where is it made?

62
00:08:03,640 --> 00:08:06,720 
It's not mine, man. I told you! I'm clean!

63
00:08:09,080 --> 00:08:12,280 
Where is it made?

64
